Spanish Stock Market Extends Trading Band For NH Hoteles

-- B y   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 
2011-10-17T07:36:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-17/spanish-stock-market-extends-trading-band-for-nh-hoteles.html
Spain’s stock market extended the
trading band for shares in  NH Hoteles SA (NHH)  to 65 percent after the
company said  China ’s HNA will pay 24 percent less than
previously agreed to take a percent stake in the Spanish
company.  A pre-market auction was extended as the trading band was
widened, the stock market said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emma Ross-Thomas at 
 erossthomas@bloomberg.net  